losed:<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nswrail.net/lines/sydney-lines.html |title=Sydney Railway Lines |work=NSWrail.net |pubsliher= |author= |ste= |access-date= }}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|- \n! Line name !! Station/platform name !! Opened !! Closed !! Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=5 | [[Olympic Park railway line#Abattoirs line|Abattoirs Branch]] ||[[Pippita railway station|Pippita]]|| 4 October 1940 || 9 November 1984 ||\n|-\n| Metropolitan Meat Platforms ||  ||  ||\n|-\n| Abattoirs Platform ||  ||  ||\n|-\n| Brickworks Platform ||  ||  ||\n|-\n| Saleyards Platform ||  ||  ||\n|-\n| rowspan=7| [[Camden railway line, New South Wales|Camden]] || Maryfields || March 1937 || 1 January 1963 || Opened as Rudds Gate\n|-\n| Kenny Kill || 10 March 1882 || 1 January 1963 ||\n|-\n| Currans Hill || 10 March 1882 || 1 January 1963 ||\n|-\n| Narellan || 10 March 1882|| 1 January 1963 ||\n|-\n| Grahams Hill || 10 March 1882 || 1 January 1963 ||\n|-\n| Kirkham || 10 March 1882 || 1 January 1963 ||\n|-\n| Camden || 10 March 1882 || 1 January 1963 ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" |[[Carlingford railway line|Carlingford]]\n|[[Rosehill railway station|Rosehill]]\n|17 November 1888 \n|5 January 2020 \n|\n|-\n|[[Camellia railway station|Camellia]]\n|21 January 1885 \n|5 January 2020 \n|Camellia will be served by the [[Parramatta Light Rail]]\n|-\n|[[Rydalmere railway station|Rydalmere]]\n|20 April 1896 \n|5 January 2020 \n|Rydalmere will be served by the Parramatta Light Rail\n|-\n|[[Dundas railway station, Sydney|Dundas]]\n|20 April 1896 \n|5 January 2020 \n|Dundas will be served by the Parramatta Light Rail\n|-\n|[[Telopea railway station|Telopea]]\n|13 June 1925 \n|5 January 2020 \n|Telopea will be served by the Parramatta Light Rail\n|-\n|[[Carlingford railway line|Carlingford]]\n|20 April 1896 \n|5 January 2020 \n|Carlingford be served by the Parramatta Light Rail\n|-\n| rowspan=7| [[Sydney Freight Network|Chullora-Sefton<br/>Goods Line]] || Boshops A Platform Sig Shops Branch ||  ||